refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.parameters;




   locale



     The locale identifier. If empty, the default locale is used.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns true if the locale uses a right-to-left
 writing system, or false otherwise.

&reftitle.examples;
Checking text direction for a locale
var_dump(Locale::isRightToLeft('en-US')); // bool(false) var_dump(Locale::isRightToLeft('ar')); // bool(true)
